body:
So just like sport games (Fifa 15, MLB Baseball) create your own avicus "Ultimate Team" (Just make a list of who you think would make an amazing team on avicus and put the IGNs)

Note: This is all based on your opinion. Please no Jokes

Minimum = 12 Players
Maximum = 18 Players
Suggested:
4 Offense
4 Midfield
4 Defense

You can add any position you would like if it is really used in-game.
I'll make a team later
